title: PioneersProductions BlogTV Recordings
description:
These are all of the videos that Randy Stair (YT name: PioneersProductions) had recorded on his BlogTV (a live streaming website) account before it shut down a while ago. They're mainly just him talking about random stuff.

All of the videos are in .flv format, in the highest quality possible, and not watermarked. The file names include 1) the order that the videos where recorded in, 2) the names that Randy gave each of the videos, and 3) the date that the videos were recorded.

Enjoy!

Sincerely,
The PioneersProductions Archivist
